    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your eyes briefly becomes pools of darkness, and ghostly, flightless wings sprout from your back temporarily. Creatures other than your allies within 10 feet of you that can see you must succeed on a <strong>Charisma saving throw</strong> (DC 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Charisma modifier) or become <strong>frightended </strong>of you until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>Until the transformation ends, once on each of your turns, you can deal extra <strong>necrotic damage</strong> to one target when you deal damage to it with an attack or a spell. The extra damage equals your proficiency bonus.</p>",
